{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ba6a58eb0a","title":"歪曲和攻击反右派斗争","origin":"《广州市工商界错误的右派的言论汇编》（第一輯），中共廣州市委社會反右辦公室編印，1958年4月10日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9f80d71c9f","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1a4ad5356d","name":"广州市工商界"},{"id":"408a66ac87","name":"谭伯益"},{"id":"6e7c4a9ec1","name":"张朗莹"},{"id":"9a16912f78","name":"谭杰云"},{"id":"acbe0131b0","name":"陈成"},{"id":"b3b19c6e59","name":"彭锦昌"},{"id":"b890f5ca0f","name":"冯文轩"},{"id":"eb927ee34c","name":"薛庆霖"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7d0095111e","type":"title","text":"歪曲和攻击反右派斗争","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"991b6f2b3f","type":"authors","text":"广州市工商界薛庆霖彭锦昌谭伯益陈成谭杰云张朗莹冯文轩","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"e59a6c1e27","type":"appellation","text":"薛庆霖：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"5a09b682f7","type":"appellation","text":"领导上鼓励鸣放不要顾虑，讲错话也没有关系，但现在有些不对了，毛主席的讲话未在报章上登载以前，曾传达说毒草可以放，使一些人无边的放，现在又有所不同了，我认为言者无罪，闻者足戒，毛主席指示仍可行，对发过谬论的人应采取说服办法，未服之前不应给予行政处分。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"7c9e82ffff","type":"appellation","text":"彭锦昌：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"5f26a120f2","type":"appellation","text":"要人家鸣放，现在一讲就要驳人，叫人怎讲呀。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"3023a1ef99","type":"appellation","text":"谭伯益：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"e92d45a889","type":"appellation","text":"由于潘以和比较突出，又是资产阶级分子，于是就搵他出来做典型，其实潘是没有反党、反社会主义的行动。章乃器很难看出是右派分子，章学问高深，在全国人代会上四川省代表集中向章驳斥，反被章驳返转头、无言以对，正如章自己所讲骨头化咗灰也找不出有丝毫反党反社会主义的痕迹。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"50012f6b1c","type":"appellation","text":"陈成：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"4f7561f2cc","type":"appellation","text":"潘以和右派思想是有，佢主要是对过去税收等不满，且一贯嘅，但呢的是税局个别同志的不对呀！不应不满，佢最不对系呢度，但反社会主义行为系冇嘅。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"d276093e43","type":"appellation","text":"谭杰云：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"54ac1d4fa5","type":"appellation","text":"令日斗人，明日斗我，今日揭发人即是揭自己，这个那个敢保证唔会做右派，大家都唔知架。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"16c61aa7bd","type":"appellation","text":"冯文轩：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"},{"id":"a8ce27c4b7","type":"appellation","text":"都算无阴功（注：指斗争右派分子黄永安），在市联开了十九个年（上午或下午），在群众压力下承认了反党反人民的罪行，这不算，还要掹（拉）去省联，又要捱二十个午，连我非定息户去开会也陪他苦一分。","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a"}],"page":{"id":"5685d61be5","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"ba6a58eb0a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}